OL,5,G0710 Our Guy in Japan
OL,6,     FGuy Martin visits a slum in
OL,7,     FYokohama, pays his respects at
OL,8,     FHiroshima and takes a dip in a
OL,9,     Fmildly radioactive spring, and
OL,10,     Fparticipates in one of Japan's
OL,11,     Foldest fireworks festivals.
OL,12,G0800 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FAustin Metro/Fiat 850 Coupe: A
OL,14,     Fcollection of Austin Mini Metros
OL,15,     Farrive for auction. Also under the
OL,16,     Fhammer is a baby Fiat 850 coupe
OL,17,     Fand a haulier offloads part of his
OL,18,     Fvintage vehicle collection.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
