OL,5,G0100 Find It, Fix It, Flog It
OL,6,     FNew. Henry Cole refurbishes a
OL,7,     Fclassic Ford Mustang and a neon
OL,8,     Fgarage sign, while Simon O'Brien
OL,9,     Frestores a classic Chopper bicycle
OL,10,     Fand turns a bass guitar into a
OL,11,     Fchair.
OL,12,G0200 Our Guy in Japan
OL,13,     FGuy Martin finds out how Japan
OL,14,     Fdeals with 1500 earthquakes a
OL,15,     Fyear, enters the gang culture of
OL,16,     FTokyo, and tries the unique form
OL,17,     Fof Japanese speedway first-hand.
